[[[that-s-it|仅此而已]]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="description"]]
//他在那站了一会，最终脑袋里只剩下了对[[span class="ruby"]]WAN[[span class="rt"]]神明[[/span]][[/span]]的感谢。//
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="title"]]
[[[origin-bullet-t3y44-ml520-sh28j|‘起源弹’(T3Y44/ML520/SH28J)]]]
[[/div]]
